Test Case: SauceDemo Positive Login Scenario

Description: Verify that a user can successfully log in to SauceDemo with valid credentials.

Pre-conditions:
- The user is on the SauceDemo login page (https://www.saucedemo.com/).

Test Steps:
1. Open the browser and navigate to https://www.saucedemo.com/
2. Enter "standard_user" in the Username field.
3. Enter "secret_sauce" in the Password field.
4. Click the "Login" button.

Expected Result:
- The user should be redirected to the inventory page (https://www.saucedemo.com/inventory.html).
- The "Products" header should be visible on the page.
- The shopping cart icon should be visible.

Post-conditions:
- The user is logged into the application.


--------------------------------------------------
Test Case: SauceDemo Logout After Successful Login

Description:
Verify that a logged-in user can successfully log out from the SauceDemo application.

Pre-conditions:
- The user is logged into SauceDemo using valid credentials.
- The inventory page is displayed.

Test Steps:
1. Click on the menu (hamburger) icon on the top-left corner.
2. Click on the "Logout" option.

Expected Result:
- The user should be logged out successfully.
- The user should be redirected to the SauceDemo login page (https://www.saucedemo.com/).
- The Username and Password fields should be visible.

Post-conditions:
- The user is logged out of the application.
